<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Reports on Incidents of Violence Continue </PHRASE></F></HT>
<H4>    Suspected Collaborator Killed in Tulkarm </H4>

<F P=102> TA2806044994 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in English 0400 GMT 28 
Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA2806044994 </F>
<F P=104>  Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] In Tulkarm, masked gunmen last night shot and 
killed a local resident who allegedly cooperated with Israeli 
authorities. Two other people who were with the man were 
wounded. A Qol Yisra'el reporter says that the gunmen entered a 
house and opened fire. The army is investigating the incident. 

</TEXT>

