<H3> <TI>   Security Services Kill 2 Involved in Assassination </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Security Services Kill 2 Involved in Assassination </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD2706222294 Algiers ENTV Television Network in Arabic 1900 
GMT 27 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2706222294 </F>
<F P=104>  Algiers ENTV Television Network </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The security services announced that yesterday they 
killed the two terrorists who assassinated the late Abdelkader 
Alloula. These two terrorists, together with a third, 
assassinated a policeman yesterday in Oran near the Bouakeul 
stadium. The operation allowed the security services to recover 
an automatic revolver, a machine gun, and other ammunition. 
  The security services also killed 14 terrorists between 
Thursday and Saturday and recovered a large quantity of weapons. 
  The security services also announced that Mr. Lakhdar 
Toumi--age 51, an imam, and the father of nine children--was 
assassinated on Friday [24 June] in Medea Province inside the 
Abu Bakr Siddik mosque as he was giving the Friday sermon. 

</TEXT>

