  [Text] During the course of a clearing up operation, 
mojahedin and forces of the Islamic army in Samangan Province 
pushed back the Golboddin-Dostam militia as far as 8 km. 
  One of the country's responsible security sources told the 
Bakhtar Information Agency that forces of the Islamic army and 
mojahedin cleared a large area of Samangan Province from the 
