<F P=100> Egypt </F>
<H3> <TI>   Source Denies `Terrorist' Injured in Suhaj </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Source Denies `Terrorist' Injured in Suhaj </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   NC2706210994 Cairo MENA in Arabic 2000 GMT 27 Jun 94 </F>
<F P=103> NC2706210994 </F>
<F P=104>  Cairo MENA </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Cairo, 27 Jun (MENA)--A ranking security source 
denied a report aired by a foreign radio today, which said a 
terrorist was injured in a clash with security forces in Suhaj. 
The source described the report as groundless and totally 
untrue. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

