  [Text] The secretary of the General People's Committee for 
Foreign Liaison and International Cooperation received this 
morning Ahmad Bakomo, ambassador of the Republic of Mali, Assimi 
Alkaidi [Toure], ambassador of the Republic of Niger, and Poli 
Porcpie [as heard], ambassador of Burkina Faso to the Great 
Jamahiriyah. 
