Mali, Niger, and Burkina Faso during their recent visits to the 
Great Jamahiriyah. The meetings also dealt with aspects of 
bilateral cooperation between the Great Jamahiriyah and these 
countries and ways to bolster them so as to serve mutual 
interests and the interests of these African states and reaffirm 
their links and cooperation with the Arab Maghreb Union. 

