<H3> <TI>   Assembly Speaker, Turkish Official Confer </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Assembly Speaker, Turkish Official Confer </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   JN2906113894 Baghdad Republic of Iraq Radio Network in 
