  [Text] National Assembly Speaker Sa'di Mahdi Salih today 
met with Muhammad Gulcegun, member of the Turkish parliament and 
deputy chairman of the Turkish Social Democratic Populist Party 
[title as heard], and his accompanying delegation. 
  The National Assembly speaker reviewed the impact of the 
