<H3> <TI>   Rabbani Said Ready To Hand Over Power </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Rabbani Said Ready To Hand Over Power </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD2906105594 Tehran Voice of the Islamic Republic of Iran 
First Program Network in Persian 0930 GMT 29 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2906105594 </F>
<F P=104>  Tehran Voice of the Islamic Republic of Iran 
First Program Network </F>

<F P=105>  Persian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] President Borhanoddin Rabbani of Afghanistan 
announced his readiness last night to hand over power to a 
transitional government. According to a report of the Central 
News Unit from Kabul, Rabbani announced that while attending the 
Herat meeting, to be held among various Afghan group leaders, he 
will hand over power to the person elected by this meeting. 
  Rabbani's term of office ended yesterday, but the Supreme 
Court of Afghanistan has demanded that Rabbani stay in power for 
another six months. 

</TEXT>

