<H3> <TI>   Kabul Fighting Continues; Dostam Jet Downed </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Kabul Fighting Continues; Dostam Jet Downed </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD2806153294 Tehran IRIB Television First Program Network in 
Persian 1430 GMT 28 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2806153294 </F>
<F P=104>  Tehran IRIB Television First Program Network </F>
<F P=105>  Persian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Today south and southeastern parts of Kabul were the 
scene of heavy clashes between the forces loyal to the president 
and supporters of Afghanistan's prime minister. At the same 
time, dozens of missiles were fired on various parts of Kabul. 
  General Dostam's fighter jets, by dropping bombs weighing 
several hundreds kg, also shook the capital of Afghanistan. 
These attacks caused considerable damage and left 13 people 
dead and wounded in the central part of Kabul. 
  Afghanistan's Defense Ministry reported that a fighter 
aircraft belonging to General Dostam was shot down. [passage 
omitted] 

