<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Tehran, June 29, IRNA -- Azeri President Geydar 
Aliyev arrived here Wednesday [29 June] heading a ranking 
political, economic, social and cultural delegation. President 
Aliyev and his entourage were welcomed at international Mehrabad 
Airport by President 'Ali Akbar Hashemi-Rafsanjani. The Azeri 
delegation will pay a four-day visit to Iran. 
  President Aliyev is being accompanied by ministers of 
foreign 
affairs, economy, national security, health, deputy prime 
minister, a number of presidential aides, head of the clerical 
bureaux of Caucasia, several parliamentarians, head of the 
Supreme Council and Nakhichevan's premier. 

