<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Prominent Islamic Lawyer Detained </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   NC2806180394 Cairo MENA in Arabic 1710 GMT 28 Jun 94 </F>
<F P=103> NC2806180394 </F>
<F P=104>  Cairo MENA </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Cairo, 28 Jun (MENA)--The Higher State Security 
Prosecution today decided to detain Lawyer Muntassir al-Zayyat 
for 15 days of interrogation under the supervision of the 
Prosecution. 
  The security department had referred al-Zayyat to the State 
Security Prosecution for interrogation about charges that he 
belongs to an extremist religious group. 
  Al-Zayyat is considered one of the most prominent lawyers 
defending the extremist Islamic groups in Egypt. 

</TEXT>

