<H3> <TI>   'Abd-al-Ghani Meets With U.S. Ambassador </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    'Abd-al-Ghani Meets With U.S. Ambassador </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   JN2806143394 Sanaa Yemeni Republic Radio Network in Arabic 
1400 GMT 28 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> JN2806143394 </F>
<F P=104>  Sanaa Yemeni Republic Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Brother 'Abd-al-'Aziz 'Abd-al-Ghani, member of the 
Presidential Council, received U.S. Ambassador Arthur Hughes in 
Sanna today. They reviewed the latest developments in Yemen, as 
well as the cease-fire initiatives that the political leadership 
has announced -- initiatives that were repeatedly violated by 
the forces of apostasy and secession. They also exchanged views 
on several issues of common interest. 

</TEXT>

