<H3> <TI>   'Arafat Closes Tunis Cultural Department Offices </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    'Arafat Closes Tunis Cultural Department Offices </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   NC2806130494 Cairo MENA in English 1245 GMT 28 Jun 94 </F>
<F P=103> NC2806130494 </F>
<F P=104>  Cairo MENA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Tunis, June 28 (MENA) -- The PLO Cultural Department 
here has been closed and its headquarters handed over to the 
owners. The closure came in implementation of PLO Chairman 
Yasir 'Arafat's decision to shut down all the organization's 
departments in the Tunisian capital except the political one. 
  Personnel will move to the self-rule area of Gaza and 
Jericho 
to start their mission there within the context of the 
Palestinian autonomy. 

</TEXT>

