Chechen state security department told INTERFAX that Russian 
troops are being redeployed today on the border of the republic. 
Khamid Zhemoldayev, deputy head of the department, says that 
special units of the Russian Ministry of Internal Affairs, equal 
to an army division, have arrived in Prigorodnyy Rayon of North 
Ossetia. 
