<F P=100> National Affairs </F>
<H3> <TI>   Fault at Nuclear Power Plant Corrected </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Fault at Nuclear Power Plant Corrected </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD3005181694 Kiev Radio Ukraine World Service in Ukrainian 
1600 GMT 30 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD3005181694 </F>
<F P=104>  Kiev Radio Ukraine World Service </F>
<F P=105>  Ukrainian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The generator of power unit No. 1 at Khmelnitskiy 
nuclear plant was disconnected for several hours. The plant 
information center reports that this was caused by false 
activation of the modular transformer containment system due to 
a short circuit in the control cable conductors. The generating 
set was reconnected upon the removal of the defect. The 
conditions of the plant's safe operation were not affected. The 
radiation situation is unchanged. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

